58
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:50,759
Okay.

59
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:16,839
Fatty.

60
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,160
Don't move. Stop.

61
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,040
