62
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:28,959
What's going on?

63
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,879
Nothing's wrong.

64
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:32,759
Let me take a look.

65
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:38,120
Big Fatty.

66
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,040
