67
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,839
N-no, it doesn't hurt.

68
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:43,439
Why is your heel bleeding?

69
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,040
You have it too.

70
00:05:50,199 --> 00:05:51,160
What's going on?

71
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:53,560
What's happening?

72
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,600
